title: Oil spill risks for Great Australian Bight outlined in Wilderness Society modelling
text: Scientific modelling shows any oil spill in the Great Australian Bight would devastate southern Australia's fishing and tourism industries, the Wilderness Society says as it warns of the ramifications of letting BP set up offshore wells. ...
